\begin{eqnarray}
\label{eq:fbulk}
f_{{\rm bulk}} &\equiv& 
4\lambda^{3/2}\cot^{-1}(\lambda^{3/2}) - 6 \ln \lambda -1 
\nonumber\\
&&+ \Big( 3 + \frac{1}{\lambda^3} \Big) \ln (1+\lambda^3).
\end{eqnarray}
The first three terms in Eq.~(\ref{eq:Fusb}) scale as $S$, whereas the rest are bulk terms that scale as $V$~\cite{footnote:anisotropy}. 
